These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, grey, black, white
1. the person who likes white is not to the right of the person who likes emerald##8
2. the person who likes white is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the german##3
4. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person who likes grey##5
5. the mexican is not to the left of the person who likes white##8
6. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
7. the chinese is somewhere between the brazilian and the person who likes grey##7
8. the chinese and the person who likes white have the same parity positions##9
9. the german and the person who likes emerald have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | chinese | german     | mexican |
| Pet           | black   | white     | grey | emerald  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, tea
There 4 different types of food: garlic, radish, papaya, peas
1. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person eating peas and the person drinking coffee have the same parity positions##9
3. the person eating radish is not to the right of the person eating papaya##8
4. the person eating garlic is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
5. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
8. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola    | almond-milk | coffee    |
| Hobby      | garlic | radish | papaya      | peas |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, horse, bird, rabbit
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, mango, pumpkin
1. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
8. the owner of the horse and the person eating avocado have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | horse    | bird   | fish    | rabbit  |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin | artichoke | mango |

