1. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the photographer is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
4. the engineer and the person watching scientific movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching superhero movies and the engineer have different parity positions##9
6. the photographer is not to the left of the person watching animation movies##8
7. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
8. the person watching documentary movies is not to the right of the lawyer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | animation | scientific | superhero |
| Nationality   | lawyer        | photographer    | engineer   | videographer |

