.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, musical, adventure, western
4 different pets are kept: fish, hamster, mouse, rabbit
1. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the owner of the hamster##7
2. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person watching musical movies is not the owner of the fish##6
6. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5
7. the person watching western movies and the owner of the rabbit have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | western | musical | time-travel | adventure |
| Pet     | hamster     | mouse     | rabbit     | fish    |

