3. the owner of the cat is the person eating strawberry##1
4. the owner of the frog and the person eating lettuce have different parity positions##9
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | strawberry | asparagus | grapefruit   | lettuce   |
| Hobby   | cat  | lizard   | frog | pony |

