.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, amaryllis, sunflower, bellflower
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, italian, turkish
1. the person who growsbellflower is not the turkish##6
2. the turkish is not to the right of the canadian##8
3. the person who growssunflower is not to the left of the person who growsbellflower##8
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the italian##3
6. the turkish is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
8. the person who growsorchid is the colombian##1
9. the person who growsbellflower and the canadian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | amaryllis   | bellflower    | sunflower | orchid    |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian | italian   | colombian |

