.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-15::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, peach, potato, tomato
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, fanta, water
1. the person eating peach and the person drinking water have the same parity positions##9
2. the person drinking water is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
3. the person eating mango is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking water##7
4. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person eating mango##7
5. the person drinking lemonade is not the person eating tomato##6
6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating mango##1
7. the person eating potato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | tomato | mango | peach | potato  |
| Music-Genre   | soy-milk    | lemonade | water | fanta |

