2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person traveling to rome is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
4. the person traveling to prague is not to the right of the person traveling to paris##8
5. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the hedgehog and the person traveling to nizza have the same parity positions##9
7. the owner of the cat and the person traveling to rome have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | nizza | prague | paris | rome |
| Pet   | hedgehog    | fish   | rat        | cat            |

