2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person eating spinach and the person who's hobby is skydiving have the same parity positions##9
5. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | lettuce    | spinach | onion | mango |
| Hobby      | puzzles | skydiving   | board-games   | baking   |

